com.android.build.api.attributes

Interface ProductFlavorAttr

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Named

    public interface ProductFlavorAttr
extends Named
    Type for the attribute holding ProductFlavor information.

    There can be more than one attribute associated to each Configuration object, where each represents a different flavor dimension.

    The key should be created with Attribute.of(dimensionName, ProductFlavorAttr.class)
